-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Server Configuration

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Database (MySQL via Prisma)

형식: mysql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE

로컬 MySQL 설정에 맞게 user, password를 변경해주세요.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

DATABASE_URL="mysql://root:password@localhost:3306/bookstore_db"

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Redis (For JWT Token Management)

형식: redis://[:password@]HOST:PORT

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

REDIS_URL="redis://localhost:6379"

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

JWT Authentication

보안을 위해 배포 시에는 반드시 복잡한 랜덤 문자열로 변경해야 합니다.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

JWT_SECRET=dev_secret_key_change_in_production_1234
JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRATION=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRATION=7d

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Security & CORS

프론트엔드 개발 서버 주소 (예: React/Vue/Svelte 등)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
BCRYPT_SALT_ROUNDS=10